<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall prescribe regulations to carry out the Educational Assistance Program.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc4157b38-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/100/322/tII/s216/b">Pub. L. 100–322, title II, § 216(b)</ref>, <date date="1988-05-20">May 20, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/529">102 Stat. 529</ref>, § 4333; renumbered § 7633, <ref href="/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/1">Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="1991-05-07">May 7, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/238">105 Stat. 238</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s4/b/1">Pub. L. 102–83, § 4(b)(1)</ref>, (2)(E), <date date="1991-08-06">Aug. 6, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/404">105 Stat. 404</ref>, 405.)</sourceCredit>
